Chess App.

# Live session - https://excalidraw.com/#room=0f08d53a928994754044,cYKwApQlMeTosanYR9BAKw

To Start.
client - npm run dev
server - npm run dev
mongo - net start mongoDB port-27017
posgresql - psql -h localhost -p 51000 -U postgres

