 Data validation (e.q. JOI)
 Cache Invalidations
 API Versioning.
 API Gateway
 Password Encryption.
 User Analytics (Google Analytics or Mixpanel)
  - steps
  mkdir server
  cd server
  npm init -y
  npm install express
  npm install --save-dev typescript @types/node @types/     express ts-node
  npx tsc --init

